Package: processmine
Title: Production-Grade Process Mining in R and Python
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Dave", "Mason", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                   email = "davidmason720@gmail.com")
Description: R interface to the processmine event-log schema: read/write XES and
    Parquet files, validate the canonical schema, discover process models,
    check conformance, analyse performance, and interoperate with the Python
    ML layer via shared Parquet files.
